<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$guan-mao-12" href="/people/guan-mao-12">关毛</a>，<strong title="动物" class="zu-question-my-bio">动物</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="115">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yao-ze-lin" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yao-ze-lin" class="zg-link" title="姚泽林">姚泽林</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$li-ping-fan-71" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/li-ping-fan-71" class="zg-link" title="李平凡">李平凡</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$he-he-97-56" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/he-he-97-56" class="zg-link" title="何和">何和</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1694425" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">谢邀。<br><br>操曰：“今天下英雄，惟使君与操耳！” <br>备听毕，拜曰：“不瞒明公。汉室倾颓，天下纷争，备实有英雄之志。然半生流离，一事无成。自愧不才，今逢曹公，方见忠臣豪杰，备愿为辅弼，佐明公成齐桓之业。”<br>操曰：“玄德果有此心？”<br>备曰：“肺腑之言，若备有丝毫欺瞒，当为白面书生所败，死于蛮夷之地。”<br>操大喜，即遣备率军讨袁术，备遂斩车胄再据徐州。<br>备大笑曰：“世人称操贼为阿瞒，孰料为我所诳，大慰吾心。蛮夷之地岂有白面书生，白面书生有岂是我之对手。”<br>……<br>白帝城<br>……<br>先主嘱托完毕，大喝三声“嘴贱”，吐血而崩。<br>白帝城，古蛮夷之地也。<br>陆逊……
